						<summary>

						<p>Damaged at the right end. It records a gift of land most probably to the temple of Sri Kailāsamuḍaiyanāyaṉār at Paruttippaḷḷi in Nāḍāḻvāṉ-nāḍu by certain individuals to conduct festival for their welfare. The donated land was located on the eastern side of the big tank.</p>						

						</summary>
